{
  "stem": "7273.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was actually, by profession, a policeman that my father sort of taught in the art of managing things, and so on, that he ended up to have owned his own four properties.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he-- he was a good pupil, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he brought her money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were good to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even food, which helped a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I personally found out after the war that he was an SS man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to me-- because I suppose my parents were so outstanding to him and made something out of him-- he was exceptional decent.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I was in the concentration camp, and through sort of the back doors, I was a painter, and I said, would you take a letter for me?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he took the letter, and I had contact with this Wagner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was so nice that he brought to the painter food for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the painter brought it in in the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- you know, at that time, I didn't know who he is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I didn't know what influence he had, because he also, while I was in the camp, through him, he made contact.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He found out where my brother is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How my brother is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So actually, I couldn't fault him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this Gustaf Wagner, who-- who was German and who you subsequently found out was in the SS, for you--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After-- after the war, I found that out, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To-- to that that extent, when I escaped from the camp and I came to him, then today I understand why he couldn't keep me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It would have been-- for him it would have been a question of life and death when I would have been discovered.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
